[![Tonight is the annual Hong Kong candle light vigil for commemorating the
June 4 Tiananmen Massacre in 1989. "Hong Wrong" have written a summary of
controversies over the theme of this year's vigil at the eve of the 24th
Anniversary.](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2013/06/candle-375x150.jpg)](http://hongwrong.com/hong-kong-
candlelit-vigil/)

今晚（6月4日）是香港弔念1989年六四天安門的年度燭光追思會。在這個24週年的燭光追思會前夕，Hong Wrong寫了一篇關於此議題爭議的概要。

